    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hydraulic structures designed to store water for various purposes, including drinking, bathing, irrigation, fire suppression, and industrial processes. Water tanks may be of various sizes and materials, but the term is generally used for structures or containers of relatively larger size.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
